text: First time eating here. I decided to try their Mee Goreng to pack home. It's pretty good. It's not too spicy but flavorful. Quite a large portion too. Love the Indian Red Sauce which had a bite, and cucumber. Am a new fan. üòÅ

Fluffy Prata, prefer mine crispier, was perfect for the wife

Loved the fish curry, thick, flavourful

Keep it up
Nice crispy prata and a bit fluffy inside. Thick type of curry to dip the prata. Shiok. Cdc vouchers accepted.
Tried the roti prata egg onion with fish curry. Really super crispy and nice. If you take with kopi siew siew dai, the combination was ideal.
